title: Man shot to death in Pasco identified
text:
PASCO, Wash. (AP) â€” The Franklin County Coroner's Office has identified an 18-year-old man fatally shot in the head in Pasco.
The Tri-City Herald reports ( http://goo.gl/EsPRPi ) Gregory G. Thacker , known as George, died soon after he was found Wednesday evening near the cable bridge.
Detectives continue to investigate.
